import React from 'react'

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Nav>
                <NavbarContainer>
                    <NavLogo>Connor Rosenberg</NavLogo>
                    <NavMenu>
                        <NavItem>
                            <NavLinks>
                                About Me
                            </NavLinks>
                        </NavItem>
                        <NavItem>
                            <NavLinks>
                                CS Projects
                            </NavLinks>
                        </NavItem>
                        <NavItem>
                            <NavLinks>
                                Extracurriculars
                            </NavLinks>
                        </NavItem>
                        <NavItem>
                            <NavLinks>
                                About Me
                            </NavLinks>
                        </NavItem>
                    </NavMenu>
                </NavbarContainer>
            </Nav>
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
